Important Notice:

This repository documents a network reconnaissance exercise performed against
Metasploitable, a deliberately vulnerable virtual machine, for EDUCATIONAL and
AUTHORIZED SECURITY TESTING purposes only.

- The techniques and findings described here should only be applied to systems
  You own or have explicit written authorization to test.
- Unauthorized scanning, enumeration, or exploitation of systems you do not own
  Control may violate computer misuse laws in your jurisdiction.
- The author assumes no liability for any misuse of the information contained
  in this repository.
- This project is intended to demonstrate learning and understanding of
  reconnaissance concepts, not to serve as an attack tool.
